<title>三级片还能获奖？没错，三个丈夫，以性来讽刺社会，侧面讲述性瘾患者的故事</title>
<link>http://www.t66y.com/read.php?tid=3727857</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.t66y.com/read.php?tid=3727857</guid>
<description>首先简单介绍一下，这部片子全程无尿点，不论从剧情上，还有伦理现实上，都能说得上是上好制作。&lt;br/&gt;它没有所谓的绿帽情节，也没有所谓的淫秽概念，唯一有的就是让小妹好好的活下去，每个人都很真诚，你可以看到&lt;br/&gt;三个所谓的丈夫，为了解决小妹的性瘾病，跑各种地方来卖淫，甚至说最后被迫无奈拿鳝鱼来解决小妹的生理问题，现实，社会，人群，思想，无一不让人疯狂，却又没有那么激荡不去，看完后只有两个字来表达，好看。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18431252.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18431252.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18432292.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18432292.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18433337.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18433337.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18433935.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18433935.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18434757.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18434757.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18435311.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18435311.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18440037.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18440037.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18440525.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18440525.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18441588.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18441588.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18441984.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18441984.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18442932.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18442932.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18443736.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18443736.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18444234.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18444234.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18445085.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18445085.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18445795.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18445795.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18450633.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18450633.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18451045.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18451045.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18451785.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18451785.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;img data-link=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/i/?i=u/20191127/18452175.png&quot; data-src=&quot;https://www.louimg.com/u/20191127/18452175.png&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;别问叫啥了，标题不都写了，三个丈夫或者三夫都是&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;[ 此貼被金刚不仅刚在2019-11-27 22:10重新編輯 ]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
